<p><a name="Equipment_for_dealing_with_sound" id="Equipment_for_dealing_with_sound"></a></p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline">Equipment for dealing with sound</span></h2>
<p>Equipment for generating or using sound includes <a href="/wiki/Musical_instrument" title="Musical instrument">musical instruments</a>, <a href="/wiki/Hearing_aid" title="Hearing aid">hearing aids</a>, <a href="/wiki/Sonar" title="Sonar">sonar</a> systems and <a href="/wiki/Sound_reproduction" title="Sound reproduction" class="mw-redirect">sound reproduction</a> and broadcasting equipment. Many of these use electro-acoustic transducers such as <a href="/wiki/Microphone" title="Microphone">microphones</a> and <a href="/wiki/Loudspeaker" title="Loudspeaker">loudspeakers</a>.</p>
<p><a name="References" id="References"></a></p>
